## ðŸŒŸ Features
- **Responsive Design**: Works seamlessly on desktop, tablet, and mobile.
- **Interactive Sections**: Hero video with typewriter effect, parallax video section, animated counters.
- **Mega Menus**: Dropdown menus for About Us and Solutions sections.
- **Projects Showcase**: Display of multiple project case studies with navigation.
- **Contact & Forms**: Integrated forms for energy assessment requests and general contact.
- **Team & Career Sections**: Highlight team members and career opportunities.
- **Social Integration**: LinkedIn and Instagram links.
- **Optimized Performance**: Smooth scrolling, lazy-loaded video and images.

## ðŸ›  Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React.js, React-Bootstrap, CSS
- **Styling**: Tailwind / Custom CSS
- **Video & Media**: HTML5 video, parallax sections
- **Forms**: Integrated with FormSubmit.co for backend-free form submission
- **State Management**: React Hooks (`useState`, `useEffect`) for interactivity
- **Animations & Effects**: Typewriter effect, scrolling-based navbar changes, hover effects

